  "title": "IT Support, Security Systems",
  "description": "<p><strong>[Job ID: 1123579] </strong><br>\n<br>\n<strong>Responsibilities</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Install, manage, and troubleshoot <strong>security systems,</strong> including <strong>Access Control</strong>, <strong>Intercom</strong>, <strong>CCTV</strong>, <strong>NAS</strong>, and <strong>VMS</strong>.</li>\n  <li>Handle <strong>cabling and electrical works</strong> such as copper/fibre installation, conduits, and trunking.</li>\n  <li>Support <strong>testing, commissioning, and maintenance</strong> of security systems.</li>\n  <li>Perform <strong>on-site troubleshooting</strong> and provide <strong>technical support and training</strong>.</li>\n  <li>Assist in <strong>network setup, system design</strong>, and configuration for security systems.</li>\n  <li>Deliver equipment and assist <strong>Project Managers/Engineers</strong> with assigned tasks.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Minimum <strong>2 years’ experience</strong> with <strong>ELV systems</strong> (Access Control, Intercom, CCTV).</li>\n  <li>Strong understanding of <strong>computer networking</strong> setup and troubleshooting.</li>\n  <li>Good knowledge of the <strong>Microsoft Windows environment</strong>.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>We regret that only shortlisted candidates will be notified. However, rest assured that all applications will be updated to our resume bank for future opportunities.<br>\n<br>\nPlease kindly refer to the Privacy Policy of Good Job Creations for your reference: https://goodjobcreations.com.sg/en/privacy-policy/<br>\n<br>\nEA Personnel Name: Ong Kang Quan Ryan<br>\nEA Personnel Registration Number: R23116952<br>\nEA License No.: 07C5771</p>",
